headline: Cessna SkyCourier Achieves Canada Type Certification, Bringing Operational Support to Remote Regions of North America
summary: WICHITA, Kan., December 17, 2024--Textron Aviation's twin-engine, large-utility turboprop, Cessna SkyCourier, has been awarded type certification by Transport Canada Civil Aviation.

headline: BAE Systems Secures $656M Deal for M2A4 and M7A4 Combat Vehicles
summary: BAESY clinches a contract for the construction of M2A4 and M7A4 combat vehicles.
